data.description: BUYER OPTIONS & SELLER INCENTIVES! FULL HOME WATER FILTRATION SYSTEM! Need lower payments? Ask us about 2-year buydown. Need lower rate for the full term? Ask us about 30-year buydown. Need closing costs in general? Ask us about seller funds to close. Your new home is HERE! Located near the Atlanta airport! This stunning property is only two years old and move-in ready, offering a contemporary design and an abundance of desirable features.  Situated on a spacious cul-de-sac lot, this home boasts privacy and tranquility. The flat back yard is perfect for outdoor activities and is fully fenced, providing a safe space for children and pets to roam freely. But that's not all - in addition to the fenced yard, there is even more land to explore!  Step inside and discover a thoughtfully designed interior with five bedrooms in total. Four of the bedrooms are located upstairs, while one is conveniently situated on the main level. The primary bedroom is oversized, providing ample space for relaxation and rest. The accompanying primary closet is also generously sized, offering plenty of storage for your wardrobe and personal belongings.  The open concept design of the main living area creates an inviting atmosphere, perfect for entertaining guests or spending quality time with family. Large windows throughout the home allow natural sunlight to flood every room, creating a warm and welcoming ambiance.  The kitchen features beautiful granite countertops that add a touch of elegance to the space. You'll have plenty of room to prepare meals and entertain loved ones. Imagine hosting gatherings and creating lasting memories in this beautiful kitchen.  For those who appreciate outdoor living, this property offers a rear patio where you can unwind and enjoy the serene surroundings. Whether you're sipping your morning coffee or hosting a barbecue, this space is perfect for creating a tranquil retreat.  The home is nestled in a brand new, just completed subdivision, ensuring a fresh and vibrant atmosphere. Additionally, there is extra parking available, providing convenience for guests and ample space for your vehicles.  Located close to shopping amenities, you'll have easy access to all the necessities and luxuries Atlanta has to offer. And for your peace of mind, this home comes with a home warranty, providing added protection and assurance.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a modern and spacious home near the Atlanta airport. Schedule a showing today and start envisioning your new life in this exceptional property!
